"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:6.2.1.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">6.2.1.1</span> 标题：䍁子、流苏（fringe, tassel）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צִיצִת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tsitsith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:38\">NUM 15:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:38\">NUM 15:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:39\">NUM 15:39</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גָּדִל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gadil)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:12\">DEU 22:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κράσπεδον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kraspedon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20\">MAT 9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:36\">MAT 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:5\">MAT 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:56\">MRK 6:56</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:44\">LUK 8:44</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0501_fringe_hans.jpg\" alt=\"流苏和下摆\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">流苏和下摆 (DRosenbach, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>以色列人会在长外袍的底边加上装饰性的流苏，特别是在长袍四角的其中一个角上。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>根据<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:37-Num15:41\">NUM 15:37–NUM 15:41</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:12\">DEU 22:12</a> 的规定，以色列人需要在外衣的四个角钉上䍁子（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">6.1 服饰（统称）（clothing [generic]）&lt;REALIA:6.1&gt;</a> ）。这些䍁子提醒他们有义务遵守摩西律法的诫命。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:5\">MAT 23:5</a> 中的希腊文<em>kraspedon</em> 是指外衣四个角上的䍁子。另外，在<em>kraspedon</em> 用来指耶稣所穿衣服的所有经文中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20\">MAT 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:36\">MAT 14:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:56\">MRK 6:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:44\">LUK 8:44</a> ），这个词可能特指䍁子，而不是仅仅指衣服的边缘。这些经文的具体解释取决于耶稣如何理解和遵行摩西律法，以及作者如何理解<em>kraspedon</em> 的意思。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:38\">NUM 15:38</a> 中，对于字面意思是“衣角上的䍁子”（“tassels on the corners”，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）的希伯来文短语，有些语言可以翻译为“带装饰的衣角”或者“衣角处的丝带”。如果目标语言没有“䍁子”一词，或者这个词含义模糊，翻译者可以采用描述性的短语；例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 将这节经文的第二句译为，“Tie several pieces of thread together and attach them to the corners of your clothes”（英文直译：“将几根线绑在一起，然后系在衣角上”）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
